            "provider": "copilot-opus46",
            "locale": "en",
            "hint": "'But' expresses directly opposite preferences of one person about two similar activities.\nThe first part `likes dancing` is a positive preference; `does not like singing` is its direct opposite. Which conjunction expresses this direct opposition?",
